At Jewelry Store In Scottsdale, AZ the solitaire setting, with its minimalist and timeless design, remains a perennial favorite among engagement ring choices. 
This classic style showcases the center diamond, allowing its natural beauty to shine without distraction. Solitaire rings effortlessly convey a sense of enduring love with sophistication and elegance. 
Because of the simplicity of the solitaire, it is easy to pair with any time of diamond shape and size providing versatility.
